trans-unit.source: Called when attributes are needed for a type.
trans-unit.target: Kalles når attributter kreves for en type.

trans-unit.source: This callback enables delayed registration of metadata attributes as well as the ability to provide code that dynamically determines which attributes should be applied.
trans-unit.target: Denne tilbakeringing aktiverer forsinket registrering av metadata attributter som muligheten til å angi koden som angir dynamisk attributter som skal brukes.

trans-unit.source: This callback is provided to the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A> method of the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder> class.
trans-unit.target: Denne tilbakeringing er angitt til <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A>metoden for <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder>klasse.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder> objects can build attributes only for the type that is requesting metadata.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder>objekter kan bygge attributter bare for typen som ber om metadata.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder>
